    slug: 'implementing-emotional-checkins-exhaustion-recovery-guide',
    title: 'Implementing Emotional Check-ins for Exhaustion Recovery: A Step-by-Step Guide to Reclaiming Your Inner Balance',
    category: 'Mental Health',
